>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:22px;flex:none;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n          <div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#a3a9b1;\">Labour of sales<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;margin-top:1px;\">{{staffingLabor}}<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#a3a9b1;\">Sales per labour hour<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;margin-top:1px;\">{{staffingSplh}}<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#a3a9b1;\">Projected hours<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;margin-top:1px;\">{{staffingHours}}<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#a3a9b1;\">Projected cost<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;margin-top:1px;\">{{staffingCost}}<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n        <sc-for list=\"{{staffing}}\" as=\"c\" hint-placeholder-count=\"6\">\n          <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:130px;border:1px solid #ece6d9;border-radius:11px;padding:13px 14px;\">\n            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:baseline;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;\">\n              <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#15293f;\">{{c.day}}<\u002Fspan>\n              <span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8a94a0;\">{{c.sales}}<\u002Fspan>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:6px;margin-top:11px;\">\n              <span class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;line-height:1;\">{{c.on}}<\u002Fspan>\n              <span style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a94a0;\">on, {{c.rec}} rec<\u002Fspan>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"margin-top:10px;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;color:{{c.statusColor}};background:{{c.statusBg}};border-radius:5px;padding:3px 8px;\">{{c.status}} {{c.gap}}<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fsc-for>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n\n      <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;margin-top:16px;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid #efe9dd;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#3c4a5a;\">Recommended cover comes from the sales forecast. Balancing the week holds labour near target.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"flex:none;\">\n          <sc-if value=\"{{staffIdle}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{true}}\">\n            <button type=\"button\" onclick=\"{{applyStaff}}\" style=\"border:none;border-radius:7px;background:#15293f;color:#fff;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;padding:10px 16px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;\" style-hover=\"background:#22364d;\">Apply the suggested shifts<\u002Fbutton>\n          <\u002Fsc-if>\n          <sc-if value=\"{{staffPlaced}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n            <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#2f6b4f;\">{{checkIcon}} Shifts updated <button type=\"button\" onclick=\"{{undoStaff}}\" style=\"margin-left:4px;font-size:12.5px;color:#6f7d8c;background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;text-decoration:underline;\">Undo<\u002Fbutton><\u002Fspan>\n          <\u002Fsc-if>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fsection>\n\n    <!-- ===== SCHEDULE QUALITY ===== -->\n    <section aria-label=\"Schedule quality\" hidden=\"{{s2Hidden}}\" style=\"order:{{ordSched}};grid-column:{{spanSched}};background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-left:4px solid #bf8a2e;border-radius:9px;padding:20px 22px;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n          <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;\">Schedule quality<\u002Fdiv>\n          <span style=\"font-size:10.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#b6831f;background:#fbf3e3;border:1px solid #ecdcb8;border-radius:5px;padding:3px 8px;\">Roadmap<\u002Fspan>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#2f6b4f;background:#eaf1ed;border:1px solid #cfe1d6;border-radius:5px;padding:3px 8px;\">Conflict detection live<\u002Fspan>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n\n      <sc-if value=\"{{schedIdle}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{true}}\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:26px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:15px;\">\n          <div>\n            <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:34px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;line-height:1;\">{{sched.copied}}<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#6f7d8c;margin-top:5px;max-width:220px;\">{{sched.sub}}<\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div>\n            <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:34px;font-weight:700;color:#b23a2e;line-height:1;\">{{sched.conflicts}}<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#6f7d8c;margin-top:5px;\">conflicts caught before sending<\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div>\n            <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:34px;font-weight:700;color:#b6831f;line-height:1;\">{{sched.cost}}<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#6f7d8c;margin-top:5px;\">unplanned cost if sent as copied<\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <sc-if value=\"{{schedHasGrid}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{true}}\">\n          <div style=\"margin-top:16px;overflow-x:auto;\">\n            <div style=\"min-width:560px;\">\n              <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:150px repeat(7, 1fr);gap:4px;margin-bottom:4px;\">\n                <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3a9b1;\">Week of 30 Jun<\u002Fspan>\n                <sc-for list=\"{{schedDays}}\" as=\"d\" hint-placeholder-count=\"7\">\n                  <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#a3a9b1;text-align:center;\">{{d.d}}<\u002Fspan>\n                <\u002Fsc-for>\n              <\u002Fdiv>\n              <sc-for list=\"{{schedGridCopied}}\" as=\"r\" hint-placeholder-count=\"6\">\n                <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:150px repeat(7, 1fr);gap:4px;align-items:center;padding:4px 0;border-top:1px solid #f3efe6;\">\n                  <div style=\"min-width:0;padding-right:6px;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:#15293f;\">{{r.name}}<\u002Fdiv>\n                    <sc-if value=\"{{r.hasNote}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n                      <div style=\"font-size:10.5px;color:#b23a2e;line-height:1.3;margin-top:1px;\">{{r.note}}<\u002Fdiv>\n                    <\u002Fsc-if>\n                  <\u002Fdiv>\n                  <sc-for list=\"{{r.cells}}\" as=\"c\" hint-placeholder-count=\"7\">\n                    <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:{{c.weight}};color:{{c.color}};background:{{c.bg}};border-radius:5px;padding:5px 2px;text-align:center;white-space:nowrap;\">{{c.t}}<\u002Fspan>\n                  <\u002Fsc-for>\n                <\u002Fdiv>\n              <\u002Fsc-for>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fsc-if>\n\n        <div style=\"margin-top:15px;border-left:3px solid #bf8a2e;background:#fcf6ea;padding:11px 14px;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n          <div style=\"font-size:13.5px;color:#3c4a5a;line-height:1.5;\">{{sched.issues}}<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <button type=\"button\" onclick=\"{{buildSchedule}}\" style=\"margin-top:16px;border:none;border-radius:8px;background:#15293f;color:#fff;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;padding:12px 18px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\" style-hover=\"background:#22364d;\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"display:inline-flex;\">{{layersIcon}}<\u002Fspan> Build from forecast<\u002Fbutton>\n        <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;color:#a3a9b1;margin-top:9px;\">The same forecast that drives your order drives your schedule. AI scheduling is roadmap. The labour matrix and conflict detection are live today.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fsc-if>\n\n      <sc-if value=\"{{schedBuilding}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n        <div style=\"margin-top:15px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\">\n          <span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"display:inline-flex;\">{{shieldIcon}}<\u002Fspan>\n          <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#2f6b4f;\">Forecast built draft, not published<\u002Fspan>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <sc-if value=\"{{schedHasGrid}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{true}}\">\n          <div style=\"margin-top:13px;overflow-x:auto;\">\n            <div style=\"min-width:560px;\">\n              <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:150px repeat(7, 1fr);gap:4px;margin-bottom:4px;\">\n                <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3a9b1;\">Resolved draft<\u002Fspan>\n                <sc-for list=\"{{schedDays}}\" as=\"d\" hint-placeholder-count=\"7\">\n                  <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#a3a9b1;text-align:center;\">{{d.d}}<\u002Fspan>\n                <\u002Fsc-for>\n              <\u002Fdiv>\n              <sc-for list=\"{{schedGridResolved}}\" as=\"r\" hint-placeholder-count=\"6\">\n                <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:150px repeat(7, 1fr);gap:4px;align-items:center;padding:4px 0;border-top:1px solid #f3efe6;\">\n                  <div style=\"min-width:0;padding-right:6px;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:#15293f;\">{{r.name}}<\u002Fdiv>\n                    <sc-if value=\"{{r.hasNote}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n                      <div style=\"font-size:10.5px;color:#2f6b4f;line-height:1.3;margin-top:1px;\">{{r.note}}<\u002Fdiv>\n                    <\u002Fsc-if>\n                  <\u002Fdiv>\n                  <sc-for list=\"{{r.cells}}\" as=\"c\" hint-placeholder-count=\"7\">\n                    <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:{{c.weight}};color:{{c.color}};background:{{c.bg}};border-radius:5px;padding:5px 2px;text-align:center;white-space:nowrap;\">{{c.t}}<\u002Fspan>\n                  <\u002Fsc-for>\n                <\u002Fdiv>\n              <\u002Fsc-for>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0;margin-top:14px;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:9px;overflow:hidden;\">\n            <sc-for list=\"{{schedSummary}}\" as=\"su\" hint-placeholder-count=\"4\">\n              <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:120px;padding:11px 14px;border-right:1px solid #f1ece1;\">\n                <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#2f6b4f;line-height:1;\">{{su.fig}}<\u002Fdiv>\n                <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;color:#6f7d8c;margin-top:4px;line-height:1.3;\">{{su.label}}<\u002Fdiv>\n              <\u002Fdiv>\n            <\u002Fsc-for>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fsc-if>\n\n        <div style=\"margin-top:15px;border:1px solid #cfe1d6;background:#f3f8f5;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;\">\n          <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#1f3d2c;line-height:1.55;\">{{sched.build}}<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:13px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n            <button type=\"button\" onclick=\"{{confirmSchedule}}\" style=\"border:none;border-radius:8px;background:#15293f;color:#fff;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;padding:11px 17px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;\" style-hover=\"background:#22364d;\">Confirm and publish<\u002Fbutton>\n            <button type=\"button\" onclick=\"{{cancelSchedule}}\" style=\"border:1px solid #cdbf9f;background:#fff;border-radius:8px;color:#6f7d8c;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;padding:11px 17px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;\">Cancel<\u002Fbutton>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;color:#8a94a0;margin-top:10px;\">Nothing publishes without your confirmation. The system does not act on its own.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fsc-if>\n\n      <sc-if value=\"{{schedResolved}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n        <div style=\"margin-top:15px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;background:#eaf1ed;border:1px solid #cfe1d6;border-radius:9px;padding:13px 15px;\">\n          <span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"display:inline-flex;\">{{checkIcon}}<\u002Fspan>\n          <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#1f3d2c;\">Schedule published. Three conflicts resolved, no unplanned overtime, labour projected down 1.8 points.<\u002Fspan>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <sc-if value=\"{{schedHasGrid}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{true}}\">\n          <div style=\"margin-top:16px;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:10px;padding:15px 17px;\">\n            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n              <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3956f;\">Labour during the shift · Tuesday 1:07pm<\u002Fspan>\n              <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#2f6b4f;\">Closing toward target<\u002Fspan>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:11px;\">\n              <div>\n                <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:30px;font-weight:700;color:#b6831f;line-height:1;\">31%<\u002Fdiv>\n                <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#6f7d8c;margin-top:4px;\">labour cost now, target 28%<\u002Fdiv>\n              <\u002Fdiv>\n              <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px;font-size:13px;color:#3c4a5a;line-height:1.5;\">Demand picks up at 1:30pm. Labour drops to about 27% without any change. No action needed unless it holds above 30% at 2pm.<\u002Fdiv>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"margin-top:12px;border-left:3px solid #bf8a2e;background:#fcf6ea;padding:10px 13px;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n              <div style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#b6831f;\">Overtime flag, 1 employee<\u002Fdiv>\n              <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#3c4a5a;line-height:1.5;margin-top:4px;\">R. Connell is in hour 7 of a 7 hour shift. Past 7:30pm it posts overtime at 1.5x. Reminder set for 7:15pm.<\u002Fdiv>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fsc-if>\n\n        <div style=\"margin-top:16px;padding-top:15px;border-top:1px solid #efe9dd;\">\n          <div style=\"font-size:13.5px;color:#3c4a5a;line-height:1.5;\">The platform saves money on food cost and labour. There is a third question.<\u002Fdiv>\n          <button type=\"button\" onclick=\"{{goDepth}}\" style=\"margin-top:11px;border:none;border-radius:8px;background:#15293f;color:#fff;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;padding:11px 17px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;\" style-hover=\"background:#22364d;\">See why it is harder to leave →<\u002Fbutton>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fsc-if>\n    <\u002Fsection>\n\n    <!-- ===== SEASONALITY & WEATHER ===== -->\n    <section aria-label=\"Seasonality and weather\" hidden=\"{{moreHidden}}\" style=\"order:{{ordSeason}};grid-column:{{spanSeason}};background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:9px;padding:20px 22px;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n        <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;\">Seasonality and weather<\u002Fdiv>\n        <span style=\"font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#bf8a2e;background:#faf2df;border:1px solid #ecdcb6;border-radius:5px;padding:3px 8px;\">Illustrative · needs integration<\u002Fspan>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n\n      <!-- week strip -->\n      <sc-if value=\"{{isWeek}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{true}}\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;margin-top:16px;\">\n          <sc-for list=\"{{weatherDays}}\" as=\"d\" hint-placeholder-count=\"7\">\n            <div style=\"flex:1;text-align:center;background:{{d.bg}};border:1px solid {{d.border}};border-radius:9px;padding:10px 3px;\">\n              <div style=\"font-size:10.5px;color:#8a94a0;\">{{d.day}}<\u002Fdiv>\n              <div aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"display:flex;justify-content:center;margin:7px 0;color:{{d.iconColor}};\">{{d.iconEl}}<\u002Fdiv>\n              <div style=\"font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#15293f;\">{{d.temp}}<\u002Fdiv>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fsc-for>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;margin-top:13px;\">\n          <sc-for list=\"{{seasonInputs}}\" as=\"ip\" hint-placeholder-count=\"3\">\n            <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:#8a5a1e;background:#fbf2e6;border:1px solid #f0e2c8;border-radius:999px;padding:5px 11px;\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"display:inline-flex;color:#bf8a2e;\">{{boltIconSm}}<\u002Fspan>{{ip.t}}<\u002Fspan>\n          <\u002Fsc-for>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;margin-top:13px;background:#fbf2ee;border:1px solid #f3ddd2;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 13px;\">\n          <span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"flex:none;margin-top:1px;color:#c2691d;\">{{historyIcon}}<\u002Fspan>\n          <div style=\"font-size:13.5px;color:#3c4a5a;line-height:1.5;\">{{season.weekNote}}<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fsc-if>\n\n      <!-- season: GP vs input cost -->\n      <sc-if value=\"{{isSeason}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n        <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a94a0;margin-top:12px;\">Gross profit per ticket against input cost across the year.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 520 190\" width=\"100%\" style=\"display:block;margin-top:10px;overflow:visible;\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Two lines across the year. Gross profit per ticket holds steady then dips through summer. Input cost rises into summer as energy and commodity costs climb, squeezing margin.\">\n          <rect x=\"200\" y=\"14\" width=\"150\" height=\"140\" fill=\"#fbf2e6\"><\u002Frect>\n          <text x=\"275\" y=\"9\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9.5\" letter-spacing=\"1\" fill=\"#bf8a2e\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">SUMMER SQUEEZE<\u002Ftext>\n          <line x1=\"30\" y1=\"154\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"154\" stroke=\"#e6e0d4\" stroke-width=\"1\"><\u002Fline>\n          <!-- input cost rising into summer -->\n          <polyline points=\"30,120 90,116 150,104 210,82 270,64 330,72 390,92 450,110 500,116\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#bf8a2e\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\u002Fpolyline>\n          <!-- GP per ticket dipping in summer -->\n          <polyline points=\"30,60 90,58 150,62 210,78 270,92 330,84 390,70 450,62 500,60\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2f6b4f\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\u002Fpolyline>\n          <circle cx=\"270\" cy=\"92\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#2f6b4f\"><\u002Fcircle>\n          <text x=\"270\" y=\"108\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#2f6b4f\">GP low<\u002Ftext>\n          <text x=\"30\" y=\"172\" font-size=\"10.5\" fill=\"#8a94a0\">Jan<\u002Ftext>\n          <text x=\"265\" y=\"172\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10.5\" fill=\"#8a94a0\">Jul<\u002Ftext>\n          <text x=\"500\" y=\"172\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"10.5\" fill=\"#8a94a0\">Dec<\u002Ftext>\n        <\u002Fsvg>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px 18px;margin-top:8px;\">\n          <span style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-size:12.5px;color:#15293f;\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:20px;height:0;border-top:3px solid #2f6b4f;\"><\u002Fspan>GP per ticket<\u002Fspan>\n          <span style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-size:12.5px;color:#15293f;\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:20px;height:0;border-top:2.4px solid #bf8a2e;\"><\u002Fspan>Input cost<\u002Fspan>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;margin-top:13px;\">\n          <sc-for list=\"{{seasonInputs}}\" as=\"ip\" hint-placeholder-count=\"3\">\n            <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:#8a5a1e;background:#fbf2e6;border:1px solid #f0e2c8;border-radius:999px;padding:5px 11px;\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"display:inline-flex;color:#bf8a2e;\">{{boltIconSm}}<\u002Fspan>{{ip.t}}<\u002Fspan>\n          <\u002Fsc-for>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;margin-top:13px;background:#fbf2ee;border:1px solid #f3ddd2;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 13px;\">\n          <span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"flex:none;margin-top:1px;color:#c2691d;\">{{historyIcon}}<\u002Fspan>\n          <div style=\"font-size:13.5px;color:#3c4a5a;line-height:1.5;\">{{season.seasonNote}}<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <sc-if value=\"{{hasGroupNote}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;margin-top:10px;background:#eef3fb;border:1px solid #d8e3f5;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 13px;\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"flex:none;margin-top:1px;color:#2f6bd8;\">{{groupIcon}}<\u002Fspan>\n            <div style=\"font-size:13.5px;color:#27425e;line-height:1.5;\">{{season.groupNote}}<\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fsc-if>\n      <\u002Fsc-if>\n    <\u002Fsection>\n\n    <!-- ===== FOOTFALL ===== -->\n    <section aria-label=\"Travel and event footfall\" hidden=\"{{s1Hidden}}\" style=\"order:{{ordFootfall}};grid-column:{{spanFootfall}};background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:9px;padding:20px 22px;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n        <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;\">Footfall drivers<\u002Fdiv>\n        <span style=\"font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#bf8a2e;background:#faf2df;border:1px solid #ecdcb6;border-radius:5px;padding:3px 8px;\">Illustrative<\u002Fspan>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a94a0;margin-top:2px;\">{{footfallSub}}<\u002Fdiv>\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 720 196\" width=\"100%\" style=\"display:block;margin-top:14px;overflow:visible;\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"{{footfallAlt}}\">\n        <line x1=\"22\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"700\" y2=\"150\" stroke=\"#e6e0d4\" stroke-width=\"1\"><\u002Fline>\n        <!-- surge band on Saturday -->\n        <rect x=\"{{ff.eventX}}\" y=\"20\" width=\"74\" height=\"130\" fill=\"#f3edfb\" opacity=\"0.6\"><\u002Frect>\n        <!-- last year -->\n        <polyline points=\"{{ff.lastYear}}\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#c4b8d8\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"4 4\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\u002Fpolyline>\n        <!-- last week -->\n        <polyline points=\"{{ff.lastWeek}}\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#aeb4bb\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\u002Fpolyline>\n        <!-- this week plan with surge -->\n        <polyline points=\"{{ff.plan}}\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2f6b4f\" stroke-width=\"3.2\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\u002Fpolyline>\n        <!-- event marker up -->\n        <circle cx=\"{{ff.eventCx}}\" cy=\"{{ff.eventCy}}\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#7a4fc0\"><\u002Fcircle>\n        <text x=\"{{ff.eventCx}}\" y=\"{{ff.eventLabelY}}\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#7a4fc0\">{{ff.eventLabel}}<\u002Ftext>\n        <!-- weather marker down -->\n        <circle cx=\"{{ff.weatherCx}}\" cy=\"{{ff.weatherCy}}\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#c2691d\"><\u002Fcircle>\n        <text x=\"{{ff.weatherCx}}\" y=\"{{ff.weatherLabelY}}\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#c2691d\">{{ff.weatherLabel}}<\u002Ftext>\n        <sc-for list=\"{{ff.dayLabels}}\" as=\"d\" hint-placeholder-count=\"7\">\n          <text x=\"{{d.x}}\" y=\"166\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#8a94a0\">{{d.label}}<\u002Ftext>\n        <\u002Fsc-for>\n      <\u002Fsvg>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:9px 16px;margin-top:8px;\">\n        <span style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-size:12px;color:#15293f;\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:18px;height:0;border-top:3px solid #2f6b4f;\"><\u002Fspan>This week plan<\u002Fspan>\n        <span style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-size:12px;color:#15293f;\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:18px;height:0;border-top:2px solid #aeb4bb;\"><\u002Fspan>Last week<\u002Fspan>\n        <span style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-size:12px;color:#15293f;\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:18px;height:0;border-top:2px dashed #c4b8d8;\"><\u002Fspan>Last year<\u002Fspan>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;margin-top:13px;\">\n        <sc-for list=\"{{footfallNotes}}\" as=\"n\" hint-placeholder-count=\"2\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"flex:none;width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:7px;background:{{n.tileBg}};color:{{n.color}};display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\">{{n.iconEl}}<\u002Fspan>\n            <span style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#3c4a5a;flex:1;min-width:0;\">{{n.text}}<\u002Fspan>\n            <span class=\"cs\" style=\"flex:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:{{n.color}};\">{{n.impact}}<\u002Fspan>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fsc-for>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:9px;margin-top:12px;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #efe9dd;\">\n        <span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"flex:none;margin-top:1px;color:#2f6b4f;\">{{bulbIcon}}<\u002Fspan>\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#2c4a39;line-height:1.45;\">{{footfallSoWhat}}<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fsection>\n\n    <!-- ===== PROMOTIONS ===== -->\n    <section aria-label=\"Promotions\" hidden=\"{{moreHidden}}\" style=\"order:{{ordPromos}};grid-column:{{spanPromos}};background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:9px;padding:20px 22px;\">\n      <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;\">Promotions<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a94a0;margin-top:2px;\">Corporate approved, with forecast impact.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:11px;margin-top:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n        <sc-for list=\"{{promotions}}\" as=\"p\" hint-placeholder-count=\"2\">\n          <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:260px;border:1px solid #ece6d9;border-radius:9px;padding:14px 15px;\">\n            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n              <div style=\"font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;color:#15293f;\">{{p.name}}<\u002Fdiv>\n              <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#2f6b4f;background:#eaf1ed;border:1px solid #cfe1d6;border-radius:5px;padding:3px 8px;\">{{checkIconSm}} Approved<\u002Fspan>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a94a0;margin-top:3px;\">{{p.window}}<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;margin-top:11px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n              <div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#a3a9b1;\">Covers lift<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;margin-top:1px;\">{{p.lift}}<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n              <div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#a3a9b1;\">Net gross profit<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#2f6b4f;margin-top:1px;\">{{p.gp}}<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n              <div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#a3a9b1;\">Stock to ready<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:{{p.stockColor}};margin-top:1px;\">{{p.stock}}<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8a94a0;margin-top:9px;padding-top:9px;border-top:1px solid #f3efe6;\">{{p.cost}}<\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fsc-for>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fsection>\n\n    <!-- ===== INDUSTRY BENCHMARKS ===== -->\n    <section aria-label=\"Industry benchmarks\" hidden=\"{{moreHidden}}\" style=\"order:{{ordBench}};grid-column:{{spanBench}};background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:9px;padding:20px 22px;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\">\n          <span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color:#6f7d8c;display:inline-flex;\">{{globeIcon}}<\u002Fspan>\n          <span class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;\">How you compare<\u002Fspan>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <span style=\"font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#bf8a2e;background:#faf2df;border:1px solid #ecdcb6;border-radius:5px;padding:3px 7px;\">Industry data · illustrative<\u002Fspan>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a94a0;margin-top:2px;\">Your numbers against target and the industry, plus commodities to watch.<\u002Fdiv>\n\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:26px;margin-top:15px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n        <!-- KPI variance table -->\n        <div style=\"flex:1.3;min-width:340px;\">\n          <div role=\"table\" aria-label=\"KPIs versus industry\">\n            <div role=\"row\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.4fr 0.8fr 0.8fr 0.8fr 0.9fr;gap:8px;padding:0 2px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #efe9dd;\">\n              <span role=\"columnheader\" style=\"font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3a9b1;\">KPI<\u002Fspan>\n              <span role=\"columnheader\" style=\"font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3a9b1;text-align:right;\">You<\u002Fspan>\n              <span role=\"columnheader\" style=\"font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3a9b1;text-align:right;\">Target<\u002Fspan>\n              <span role=\"columnheader\" style=\"font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3a9b1;text-align:right;\">Industry<\u002Fspan>\n              <span role=\"columnheader\" style=\"font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3a9b1;text-align:right;\">vs Ind.<\u002Fspan>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n            <sc-for list=\"{{benchmarks}}\" as=\"b\" hint-placeholder-count=\"6\">\n              <div role=\"row\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.4fr 0.8fr 0.8fr 0.8fr 0.9fr;gap:8px;align-items:center;padding:9px 2px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3efe6;\">\n                <span role=\"cell\" style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#15293f;\">{{b.kpi}}<\u002Fspan>\n                <span role=\"cell\" class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:13.5px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;text-align:right;\">{{b.you}}<\u002Fspan>\n                <span role=\"cell\" style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a94a0;text-align:right;\">{{b.target}}<\u002Fspan>\n                <span role=\"cell\" style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a94a0;text-align:right;\">{{b.industry}}<\u002Fspan>\n                <span role=\"cell\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;color:{{b.vsColor}};background:{{b.vsBg}};border-radius:5px;padding:2px 7px;white-space:nowrap;\">{{b.vsArrow}} {{b.vs}}<\u002Fspan><\u002Fspan>\n              <\u002Fdiv>\n            <\u002Fsc-for>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;color:#a3a9b1;margin-top:12px;\">Variance is against the industry median for comparable outlets. Green means ahead, amber means behind.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <!-- Commodity watch -->\n        <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:300px;\">\n          <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3956f;\">Commodity watch<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8a94a0;margin-top:2px;\">Where today sits against the normal price range.<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:11px;margin-top:13px;\">\n            <sc-for list=\"{{commodities}}\" as=\"c\" hint-placeholder-count=\"4\">\n              <div>\n                <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;\">\n                  <span style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#15293f;\">{{c.name}} <span style=\"font-weight:400;color:#8a94a0;\">{{c.price}}<\u002Fspan><\u002Fspan>\n                  <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:{{c.color}};background:{{c.bg}};border-radius:5px;padding:2px 8px;white-space:nowrap;\">{{c.sd}} {{c.stateLabel}}<\u002Fspan>\n                <\u002Fdiv>\n                <svg viewBox=\"0 0 260 16\" width=\"100%\" height=\"16\" style=\"display:block;margin-top:6px;\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"{{c.alt}}\">\n                  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"6\" width=\"260\" height=\"4\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"#f1ece1\"><\u002Frect>\n                  <rect x=\"{{c.bandX}}\" y=\"6\" width=\"{{c.bandW}}\" height=\"4\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"#dfe6df\"><\u002Frect>\n                  <line x1=\"130\" y1=\"3\" x2=\"130\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#c4c8d0\" stroke-width=\"1\"><\u002Fline>\n                  <circle cx=\"{{c.dotX}}\" cy=\"8\" r=\"5\" fill=\"{{c.color}}\"><\u002Fcircle>\n                <\u002Fsvg>\n                <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#6f7d8c;line-height:1.4;margin-top:5px;\">{{c.note}}<\u002Fdiv>\n              <\u002Fdiv>\n            <\u002Fsc-for>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:9px 14px;margin-top:12px;padding-top:11px;border-top:1px solid #efe9dd;\">\n            <span style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:11px;color:#6f7d8c;\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#dfe6df;\"><\u002Fspan>Normal range, plus or minus one band<\u002Fspan>\n            <span style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:11px;color:#6f7d8c;\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#b23a2e;\"><\u002Fspan>Expensive<\u002Fspan>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- ===================== FOOTER ===================== -->\n  <p style=\"margin:24px 2px 0;font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.6;color:#a3a9b1;max-width:820px;\">Ordering, waste, inventory, volumes and unit economics come from the demand engine, your recipes and live inventory. Weather, footfall and seasonality inputs are illustrative and depend on an integration. Promotions are set and approved by corporate. Industry notes are sourced externally.<\u002Fp>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:18px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid #e0d8c9;\">\n    <a href=\"https://niallfogarty.github.io/invrt-share/AI%20Agent%20Console%20(Standalone).html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;color:#6f7d8c;text-decoration:none;\" style-hover=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Agent console →<\u002Fa>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n <\u002Fdiv>\n <\u002Fsc-if>\n\n <!-- ===================== PLATFORM DEPTH ===================== -->\n <sc-if value=\"{{isDepth}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n <div data-screen-label=\"Platform depth\" style=\"max-width:1040px;margin:0 auto;padding:18px 30px 64px;\">\n   <button type=\"button\" onclick=\"{{setView}}\" data-view=\"full\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0d8c9;background:#fff;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#6f7d8c;padding:8px 13px;margin-bottom:20px;\" style-hover=\"background:#f7f4ee;\">← Back to the full picture<\u002Fbutton>\n\n   <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3956f;\">Platform depth<\u002Fdiv>\n   <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:25px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;margin-top:5px;max-width:720px;line-height:1.25;\">Why this is harder to leave than it is to buy<\u002Fdiv>\n\n   <div role=\"tablist\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-top:20px;\">\n     <sc-for list=\"{{depthPills}}\" as=\"p\" hint-placeholder-count=\"4\">\n       <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"{{p.on}}\" onclick=\"{{setDepthTab}}\" data-tab=\"{{p.key}}\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0d8c9;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:9px 15px;border-radius:999px;background:{{p.bg}};color:{{p.fg}};\">{{p.label}}<\u002Fbutton>\n     <\u002Fsc-for>\n   <\u002Fdiv>\n\n   <!-- RECIPE DNA -->\n   <sc-if value=\"{{depthRecipe}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{true}}\">\n     <div style=\"margin-top:22px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:11px;padding:26px 28px;\">\n       <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:21px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;\">What one sale depletes<\u002Fdiv>\n       <div style=\"font-size:13.5px;color:#6f7d8c;margin-top:5px;\">Classic chicken burger, traced through every ingredient the platform deducts from stock.<\u002Fdiv>\n       <div style=\"margin-top:22px;max-width:560px;\">\n         <sc-for list=\"{{recipeChain}}\" as=\"r\" hint-placeholder-count=\"7\">\n           <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:18px 1fr;gap:16px;\">\n             <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;\">\n               <div style=\"width:11px;height:11px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff;border:2px solid #2f6b4f;margin-top:18px;flex:none;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n               <sc-if value=\"{{r.notLast}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{true}}\">\n                 <div style=\"flex:1;width:2px;background:#e6e0d4;margin:3px 0;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n               <\u002Fsc-if>\n             <\u002Fdiv>\n             <div style=\"padding-bottom:10px;\">\n               <div style=\"background:#faf8f3;border:1px solid #eee9dd;border-radius:9px;padding:12px 15px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n                 <div style=\"min-width:0;\">\n                   <div style=\"font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;color:#15293f;\">{{r.name}}<\u002Fdiv>\n                   <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;color:#8a94a0;margin-top:2px;\">{{r.rule}} · yield {{r.yield}}<\u002Fdiv>\n                 <\u002Fdiv>\n                 <span class=\"cs\" style=\"flex:none;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;\">{{r.qty}}<\u002Fspan>\n               <\u002Fdiv>\n             <\u002Fdiv>\n           <\u002Fdiv>\n         <\u002Fsc-for>\n       <\u002Fdiv>\n       <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#6f7d8c;margin-top:6px;\">7 ingredients · 26 months of configuration · 104 verified counts<\u002Fdiv>\n       <div style=\"margin-top:20px;border-left:3px solid #bf8a2e;background:#fcf6ea;border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;padding:15px 18px;\">\n         <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3c4a5a;line-height:1.6;\">This depletion mapping is specific to your operation. The yield factors, costing rules and modifier configurations were set up over 26 months and verified against 104 weekly counts. Every outlet on your estate has its own version. Rebuilding it on a different platform would require starting from zero, outlet by outlet.<\u002Fdiv>\n       <\u002Fdiv>\n       <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#a3a9b1;margin-top:14px;\">Configuration depth compounds with every count. It does not transfer.<\u002Fdiv>\n     <\u002Fdiv>\n   <\u002Fsc-if>\n\n   <!-- ESTATE UNIFICATION -->\n   <sc-if value=\"{{depthEstate}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n     <div style=\"margin-top:22px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:11px;padding:26px 28px;\">\n       <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1px 1fr;gap:24px;\">\n         <div style=\"min-width:0;\">\n           <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#15293f;\">{{euLeft.head}}<\u002Fdiv>\n           <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#a3a9b1;margin-top:2px;\">{{euLeft.outlets}}<\u002Fdiv>\n           <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-top:14px;\">\n             <sc-for list=\"{{euLeft.metrics}}\" as=\"m\" hint-placeholder-count=\"3\">\n               <div style=\"background:#faf8f3;border:1px solid #eee9dd;border-radius:9px;padding:12px 14px;\">\n                 <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;color:#8a94a0;\">{{m.k}}<\u002Fdiv>\n                 <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:21px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;margin-top:3px;\">{{m.v}}<\u002Fdiv>\n               <\u002Fdiv>\n             <\u002Fsc-for>\n           <\u002Fdiv>\n         <\u002Fdiv>\n         <div style=\"background:#eee9dd;width:1px;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n         <div style=\"min-width:0;\">\n           <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#15293f;\">{{euRight.head}}<\u002Fdiv>\n           <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#a3a9b1;margin-top:2px;\">{{euRight.outlets}}<\u002Fdiv>\n           <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-top:14px;\">\n             <sc-for list=\"{{euRight.metrics}}\" as=\"m\" hint-placeholder-count=\"3\">\n               <div style=\"background:#faf8f3;border:1px solid #eee9dd;border-radius:9px;padding:12px 14px;\">\n                 <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;color:#8a94a0;\">{{m.k}}<\u002Fdiv>\n                 <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:21px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;margin-top:3px;\">{{m.v}}<\u002Fdiv>\n               <\u002Fdiv>\n             <\u002Fsc-for>\n           <\u002Fdiv>\n         <\u002Fdiv>\n       <\u002Fdiv>\n\n       <div style=\"margin-top:22px;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid #efe9dd;\">\n         <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#2f6b4f;\">Estate total<\u002Fdiv>\n         <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr);gap:12px;margin-top:12px;\">\n           <sc-for list=\"{{euTotal}}\" as=\"m\" hint-placeholder-count=\"3\">\n             <div style=\"background:#f3f8f5;border:1px solid #cfe1d6;border-radius:9px;padding:13px 15px;\">\n               <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;\">\n                 <span style=\"font-size:11.5px;color:#5a6675;min-width:0;\">{{m.k}}<\u002Fspan>\n                 <span style=\"font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#bf8a2e;background:#fbf3e3;border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;flex:none;\">Directional<\u002Fspan>\n               <\u002Fdiv>\n               <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:23px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;margin-top:4px;\">{{m.v}}<\u002Fdiv>\n             <\u002Fdiv>\n           <\u002Fsc-for>\n         <\u002Fdiv>\n       <\u002Fdiv>\n\n       <div style=\"margin-top:22px;border-left:3px solid #bf8a2e;background:#fcf6ea;border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;padding:15px 18px;\">\n         <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3c4a5a;line-height:1.6;\">These two columns run on different payment systems with different data formats. Without this platform, they cannot be compared. This estate food cost view requires a manual spreadsheet built every week. This platform has unified this estate’s POS data since 2017. Every outlet, every format, one number.<\u002Fdiv>\n       <\u002Fdiv>\n       <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#a3a9b1;margin-top:14px;\">POS agnostic since the first outlet. Mixed estate reporting from day one.<\u002Fdiv>\n     <\u002Fdiv>\n   <\u002Fsc-if>\n\n   <!-- AUDIT ANSWER -->\n   <sc-if value=\"{{depthAudit}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n     <div style=\"margin-top:22px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:11px;padding:26px 28px;\">\n       <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:21px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;\">Answer an audit in one file<\u002Fdiv>\n       <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-top:18px;\">\n         <div style=\"background:#faf8f3;border:1px solid #eee9dd;border-radius:9px;padding:13px 15px;\">\n           <div style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3a9b1;\">Outlet<\u002Fdiv>\n           <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#15293f;margin-top:4px;\">Outlet 47, Dublin City Centre<\u002Fdiv>\n         <\u002Fdiv>\n         <div style=\"background:#faf8f3;border:1px solid #eee9dd;border-radius:9px;padding:13px 15px;\">\n           <div style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3a9b1;\">Date range<\u002Fdiv>\n           <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#15293f;margin-top:4px;\">1 January 2026 to 31 March 2026<\u002Fdiv>\n         <\u002Fdiv>\n       <\u002Fdiv>\n       <div style=\"background:#faf8f3;border:1px solid #eee9dd;border-radius:9px;padding:13px 15px;margin-top:14px;\">\n         <div style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a3a9b1;\">Record types<\u002Fdiv>\n         <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#15293f;margin-top:4px;\">Temperature logs, HACCP checks, Allergen verifications, Checklist completions<\u002Fdiv>\n       <\u002Fdiv>\n\n       <sc-if value=\"{{auditIdle}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{true}}\">\n         <button type=\"button\" onclick=\"{{runAudit}}\" style=\"margin-top:18px;border:none;border-radius:8px;background:#15293f;color:#fff;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;padding:12px 18px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;\" style-hover=\"background:#22364d;\">Generate audit package<\u002Fbutton>\n       <\u002Fsc-if>\n       <sc-if value=\"{{auditRunning}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n         <div style=\"margin-top:18px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;\">\n           <span class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:30px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;\">{{auditCount}}s<\u002Fspan>\n           <span style=\"font-size:13.5px;color:#6f7d8c;\">Assembling records, every check accounted for...<\u002Fspan>\n         <\u002Fdiv>\n       <\u002Fsc-if>\n       <sc-if value=\"{{auditDone}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n         <div style=\"margin-top:18px;border-left:3px solid #2f6b4f;background:#f3f8f5;border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;padding:16px 18px;\">\n           <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\">\n             <span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"display:inline-flex;\">{{checkIcon}}<\u002Fspan>\n             <span style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#1f3d2c;\">Audit package ready in 11 seconds<\u002Fspan>\n           <\u002Fdiv>\n           <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px;margin-top:13px;\">\n             <sc-for list=\"{{auditResults}}\" as=\"a\" hint-placeholder-count=\"4\">\n               <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto auto;gap:14px;align-items:center;padding-bottom:9px;border-bottom:1px solid #e1ece5;\">\n                 <span style=\"font-size:13.5px;color:#15293f;min-width:0;\">{{a.label}}<\u002Fspan>\n                 <span class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:13.5px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;\">{{a.records}}<\u002Fspan>\n                 <span style=\"font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#2f6b4f;white-space:nowrap;\">{{a.pct}}<\u002Fspan>\n               <\u002Fdiv>\n             <\u002Fsc-for>\n           <\u002Fdiv>\n           <button type=\"button\" onclick=\"{{runAudit}}\" style=\"margin-top:14px;border:1px solid #cfe1d6;background:#fff;border-radius:8px;color:#2f6b4f;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;padding:10px 16px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;\" style-hover=\"background:#f3f8f5;\">Download audit package<\u002Fbutton>\n         <\u002Fdiv>\n       <\u002Fsc-if>\n\n       <div style=\"margin-top:22px;border-left:3px solid #bf8a2e;background:#fcf6ea;border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;padding:15px 18px;\">\n         <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3c4a5a;line-height:1.6;\">This outlet has 847 days of compliance records. Every temperature check, every checklist, every allergen verification. On demand, in one file, in eleven seconds. For a 200 outlet estate, a single failed audit can cost more than the annual subscription to this platform.<\u002Fdiv>\n       <\u002Fdiv>\n       <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#a3a9b1;margin-top:14px;\">Records accumulate daily. The longer you are on the platform, the faster you pass an audit.<\u002Fdiv>\n     <\u002Fdiv>\n   <\u002Fsc-if>\n\n   <!-- DEPENDENCY MAP -->\n   <sc-if value=\"{{depthMap}}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{false}}\">\n     <div style=\"margin-top:22px;\">\n       <div class=\"cs\" style=\"font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#15293f;\">What this platform would cost to rebuild<\u002Fdiv>\n       <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-top:18px;\">\n         <sc-for list=\"